      <div class="faq-item">
        <strong>Can I use bath bombs or bath salts?</strong>
        <p>Occasional use is fine, but rinse the surface after each bath.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <strong>What about hair dye?</strong>
        <p>Rinse immediately after use to avoid staining the finish.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item">
        <strong>How often should I clean the surface?</strong>
        <p>Weekly cleaning is ideal for maintaining shine and preventing buildup.</p>
      </div>
